<li><a href="http://www.dodccrp.org/files/Atkinson_Agile.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.dodccrp.org/files/Atkinson_Agile.pdf" rel="nofollow">The Agile Organization</a> by Atkinson and Moffat (CCRP, 2005)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.dodccrp.org/files/Alberts_Power.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.dodccrp.org/files/Alberts_Power.pdf" rel="nofollow">Power to the Edge</a> by Alberts and Hayes (CCRP, 2003)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.dodccrp.org/files/Alberts_NCW.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.dodccrp.org/files/Alberts_NCW.pdf" rel="nofollow">Network Centric Warfare</a> by Alberts et al. (CCRP, 1999)</li>
</ul>
